UPDATE courses SET
    course_description = '<p>The Bachelor of Business equips students for the ever-evolving professional landscape by providing them a comprehensive range of applied skills and knowledge necessary to thrive as future business leaders. This program offers an applied approach to business education, encompassing crucial areas such as innovation, business analytics, marketing, management, and finance. Furthermore, students have the opportunity to delve deeper into their areas of interest through a selection of majors and minors. The six distinctive majors available within the program cater to diverse career aspirations, specifically: innovation and entrepreneurship, marketing, leadership and management, human resources management, international relations, and international business. Students can choose up to two majors, or instead undertake one major and up to two minors, providing skills across three areas of business.</p><p>To ensure graduates are life-ready, the program places a strong emphasis on practical and applied learning. Case studies in the program are drawn from real-world business scenarios to provide students with a tangible understanding of the challenges and opportunities they may encounter in their careers. Authentic assessments further reinforce their ability to apply knowledge in a practical context. This combination of theory and hands-on experience equips students with a well-rounded skill set, enabling them to step into the dynamic business world with confidence and competence.</p><p>All majors are available for study at Newcastle City Precinct.</p><p>Majors offered at Ourimbah are: Marketing, Human Resource Management, Leadership and Management.</p><p>Majors offered at PSB Singapore are: Marketing, Leadership and Management and International Business.</p>',
