UPDATE courses SET
    course_description = '<p>If you are a practicing teacher or educator with a passion for learning and a desire to deepen your understanding of educational issues, the Graduate Certificate in Education is the program for you. This program will enhance your existing skills as an education professional, connect you with the latest developments and research, allow you to explore system-level challenges beyond the classroom and strengthen your leadership skills. The program also articulates into our Master of Education for the Mathematics and TESOL specialisations.</p>',
    onshore_tuition_fee = '',
    offshore_tuition_fee = '',
    entry_requirements = '<div class="css-1bxk47o-Box--Box-Box-Card--CardBody e12hqxty1"><div class="css-yd08g9-Box--Box-Box-Attribute--AttrContainer ene3w3n3" display=""><div class="css-t643gp-Attribute--AttrBody ene3w3n1" data-testid="AttrBody"><div class="css-19qn38w-Box--Box-Box-Flex--Flex-Flex e8qda2r1"> </div><div class="css-1nx81rv-Attribute--AttributeChildrenWrap ene3w3n0"><div class="css-apyj4p-Box--Box-Box-Card--CardBody e12hqxty1"><p>The Graduate Certificate in Education is a 40-unit postgraduate qualification for:</p> <p><strong>Teacher Retraining <br/></strong>Applicants with a recognised Australian teaching qualification who wish to undertake an additional teaching area* in Mathematics or TESOL must have a:</p> <ul> <li>Bachelor Degree in Education/Teaching</li> </ul> <p>*Some applicants may need to undertake more than 40 units of study in Mathematics or TESOL depending on previous tertiary studies. For these applicants, credit will be awarded into the Master of Education (Mathematics or TESOL specialisation).</p> <p><strong>Professional Learning <br/></strong>Applicants who wish to gain professional learning in TESOL must have one of the following qualifications:</p> <ul> <li>Bachelor Degree or higher; or</li> <li>Diploma or Advanced Diploma plus two years'' relevant work experience; or</li> <li>At least five years’ relevant work experience.</li> </ul> <p>Relevant work experience includes education, teaching, training, tutoring, or equivalent.</p> <p>Work experience can be demonstrated through: certified copies of all relevant qualifications, a detailed CV, and a statement of service or signed letters from employers confirming your role, duties and period of employment.</p> </div></div></div></div></div><div aria-label="English language requirements accordions" class="css-1d7k8gv-Box--Box-Box-Card--Card-Card-EmptyCard--EmptyCard-styled--SAccordionContainer e1s7etki7" elevation="2" id="Englishlanguagerequirements-3cf5a54f-e17b-4bfb-afd0-f3162060786b" n