    course_description = '<p>The Graduate Certificate in Laboratory Medicine is designed for graduates of biology, biotechnology or biomedical science degrees who are interested in a career in diagnostic pathology. Students will gain practical experience of the latest advances in diagnostic medicine and will develop the knowledge and skills to contribute to the generation of diagnostic laboratory reports. The program covers an introduction to laboratory medicine, with an emphasis on practical laboratory skills that will transfer to a modern pathology laboratory. Graduates will be prepared for employment in a diagnostic pathology laboratory. </p>',
