UPDATE courses SET
    course_description = '<p>The Graduate Certificate in Marketing and Digital Strategy equips students with essential skills for today’s evolving marketing sectors, blending foundational marketing principles with advanced digital strategies. The program provides a foundation in marketing theory, covering the principles of marketing strategy, consumer psychology and behaviour, and digital marketing strategy. Students can then choose to specialise in an area that complements their career objectives, choosing from Data-Driven Marketing Research, Media and Advertising Strategy, Marketing Analytics and Emerging Technologies, Customer Experience Management, Content Creation and Storytelling, Social Media and Mobile Marketing, or Brand Value Creation. This 40-unit certificate offers a pathway to the Master of Marketing and Digital Strategy for students wanting to deepen their expertise and enhance their strategic capabilities in the marketing field.</p>',
    onshore_tuition_fee = '',
    offshore_tuition_fee = '',
    entry_requirements = '<div class="css-1bxk47o-Box--Box-Box-Card--CardBody e12hqxty1"><div class="css-yd08g9-Box--Box-Box-Attribute--AttrContainer ene3w3n3" display=""><div class="css-t643gp-Attribute--AttrBody ene3w3n1" data-testid="AttrBody"><div class="css-19qn38w-Box--Box-Box-Flex--Flex-Flex e8qda2r1"> </div><div class="css-1nx81rv-Attribute--AttributeChildrenWrap ene3w3n0"><div class="css-apyj4p-Box--Box-Box-Card--CardBody e12hqxty1"><p>Entry into the Graduate Certificate in Marketing and Digital Strategy will be available for applicants who have one of the following qualifications:</p> <ul> <li>Bachelor degree or</li> <li>Bachelor Honours degree or</li> <li>Advanced Diploma plus 1 year relevant work experience or</li> <li>Diploma plus 2 years relevant work experience or</li> <li>3 years relevant work experience</li> </ul> <p>Relevant work experience includes: accounting, business, commerce, communication, economics, finance, human resource management, industrial relations, management, or marketing.</p> <p>Work experience can be demonstrated through certified copies of all relevant qualifications, a detailed CV, and a statement of service or signed letters from employers confirming your role, duties and period of employment.</p> </div></div></div></div></div><div aria-label="English language requirements accordions" class="css-1d7k8gv-Box--Box-Box-Card--Card-Card-EmptyCard--EmptyCard-styled--SAccordionContainer e1s7etki7" elevation="2" id="Englishlanguagerequirements-1c158a1a-f792-41b1-b2cb-fc2661b130fc" name="ACCORDION_CONTAINER" role="list"><div class="false css-rg4i61-Box--Box-Box-Flex--Flex-Flex-styled--SAccordionHeader e1s7etki6"><p style="font-weight: bold;" class="css-1b0v7mv-Accordions--HeadingWithSizing-ComponentHeading--ComponentHeading e1915jlq0"><div class="css-jshiy7-Box--Box-Box-Flex--Flex-Flex e8qda2r1">English language requirements </div></p><div class="css-1cgp17n-styled--SAccordionToggleAll e1s7etki2" id="Englishlanguagerequirements-1c158a1